content: I am a Jordanian graduate from the master’s program “Computational Mechanics” at the Technical University of Munich. During my studies, I have developed a profound knowledge in Finite Element Analysis, Material Modeling, Structural Optimization and Computational Fluid Dynamics. Also, through working in the industry part-time during my studies, I have expanded my knowledge in agile software development. Currently, I am keen to get more exposed to innovative projects through employment or PhD studies.
